      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"2. MINTER MULWEE hit the ground running from out wide and on speed early but faded and swamped late when 7th at this track in Grade 5 company. Form here at the trip sound including four wins. The form from his last run stacks up well. Better than last start and worth following up. 1. RATTLIN' IMPACT turned spotting a big start finishing fifth (23.42) last time in a Grade 4/5 at this track. The form out of his last race has been franked. One of the main contenders. 7. PHYSICALITY was strong over this course and distance last time despite filling the minors, finishing 2.5 lengths behind Kalani Sea in 23.16 and recording a new PB here. In form and must include in calculations. 4. RHAPSODY BEAST has claims fresh from a recent placing.\",\"runners\":[2,1,7,4],\"exclusive\":false}",
